high_descs: Turn right and take a step forward, then turn left and walk up to the sink.
Open the cabinet door that is below the right sink basin and take the golden spoon out, then close the door.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn right and take two steps, turn right to face the sink.
Put the golden spoon in the leftmost sink basin then turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean golden spoon.
Turn right and look down at the lower cabinets.
Open the rightmost cabinet door in front of you and put the clean golden spoon inside, then close the cabinet door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean golden spoon in a cabinet.

high_descs: Open the right cabinet beneath the sink and take out the ice cream scoop from it.
Take a step the the right towards the left sink.
Place the scoop in the sink, wash it, and take it back out.
Turn right to find the cabinet beneath the microwave.
Place the scoop in the cabinet and close it.
anns.task_desc: Place the cleaned scoop in the cabinet below the microwave.

high_descs: Move straight ahead to the sink.
Open the bottom right cabinet and remove the ladle.
Carry the ladle and take a few steps left to face the sink.
Place the ladle in the the left side of the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the ladle.
Take the ladle and turn to the right.
Open the bottom right cabinet and place the ladle inside.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a ladle and put it in a cabinet.
